title: 'Awesome phone in this price segment....dont listen to negative people'
body: 'First of all I would like to ask people who are saying negative about the phone please answer this question --- ARE YOU PEOPLE EXPECTING A SAMSUNG S23 ULTRA KIND OF A PERFORMANCE WITH A SHOE STRING BUDGET???? --- People are writing that camera is not good during low light may I ask you if you are expecting a DSLR camera pbone to be given to you at 6000-7000????  I MUST SAY THE CAMERA IS AWESOME AT THIS PRICE POINT.  people are saying processor lags....what can you expect from a 4GB RAM phone in a 5G era???  This phone is NOT FOR CAMERA OR HEAVY GAMING OR FOR MULTI APPLICATION WORK ENVIRONMENT SO.........FIRST LEARN WHAT TO EXPECT FROM A "BUDGET PHONE" AND THEN COMMENT.  FINAL VERDICT - this is an amazing phone for a regular everyday use.  Note- dont listen to negative minded people as they tgemselves dont know what they are saying.'

title: 'Best Sumsung Mobile Below 10K'
body: 'The phone meets all the expectations for the 10k price point the display is top notch and also there is no lag in performance. The photo quality is also good. Bought this phone for my Mom Good battery life ample screen size and camera quality.'

title: 'Budget phone with Certain Drawbacks'
body: 'Build and Design is Nice as far as the price is concerned. The processor is capable but lags. Heats a bit when put on multi tasking. camera is decent in Daylight. Indoors and Night time it sucks. Comes with Dedicated micro sd slot. No visible camera bump on the rear side. Overall a pocket saver. Perfect for Elders and Kids.'
